Don't let him off.

262
00:17:32.301 --> 00:17:34.678  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
Professor,
this is where you came

263
00:17:34.762 --> 00:17:37.264  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
to distance yourself from
everything that can hurt you...

264
00:17:38.891 --> 00:17:41.602  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
fleeing to the safety
of your cage.

265
00:17:43.437 --> 00:17:44.688  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
Seems to me,

266
00:17:44.772 --> 00:17:46.815  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
the thing you're
most afraid of is...

267
00:17:46.899 --> 00:17:47.941  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
the human race.

268
00:17:49.902 --> 00:17:51.987  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
[Professor] <i>Wrong</i>.

269
00:17:52.154 --> 00:17:53.655  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
Now's your chance.

270
00:17:56.867 --> 00:17:58.327  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
[Heinrich] <i>Come on. Do it</i>!

271
00:18:11.215 --> 00:18:12.674  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
[Heinrich]
<i>The station has returned</i>

272
00:18:12.758 --> 00:18:14.343  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
<i>to normal operating conditions.</i>

273
00:18:14.426 --> 00:18:16.637  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
<i>I'm going to start</i>
<i>the final purge.</i>

274
00:18:16.720 --> 00:18:18.055  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
[Joe] <i>Roger that</i>.

275
00:18:23.018 --> 00:18:26.063  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
What now, Professor?
There's time to fix this.

276
00:18:26.146 --> 00:18:28.565  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
I can still save your life,
if you so wish.

277
00:18:30.859 --> 00:18:33.028  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
[Professor]
<i>You words are meaningless.</i>

278
00:18:33.112 --> 00:18:37.574  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
<i>I fear nothing,</i>
<i>not even my own demise.</i>

279
00:18:50.337 --> 00:18:52.756  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
[Françoise]
<i>009, get to the airlock.</i>

280
00:18:52.840 --> 00:18:53.841  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
[Joe] <i>Right</i>.

281
00:19:07.312 --> 00:19:09.731  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
[Françoise] <i>When he collided</i>
<i>with the debris earlier</i>,

282
00:19:09.815 --> 00:19:12.776  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
<i>002 did calculations</i>
<i>on his trajectory</i>

283
00:19:12.860 --> 00:19:15.654  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
<i>to make sure that he could</i>
<i>get back to the station.</i>

284
00:19:15.821 --> 00:19:17.990  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
[Heinrich] <i>You wouldn't think it</i>
<i>to look at him</i>,

285
00:19:18.073 --> 00:19:19.867  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
<i>but that one's pretty cunning.</i>

286
00:19:19.950 --> 00:19:21.785  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
<i>Don't tell him I said that.</i>

287
00:19:25.455 --> 00:19:27.166  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
[Joe] <i>What's Jet's condition</i>?

288
00:19:27.249 --> 00:19:29.543  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
[Françoise] <i>To cut down</i>
<i>on his oxygen consumption</i>,

289
00:19:29.626 --> 00:19:31.420  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
<i>he put himself</i>
<i>into sleep mode.</i>

290
00:19:31.503 --> 00:19:33.964  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
<i>When he gets some air,</i>
<i>he should wake right up.</i>

291
00:19:40.220 --> 00:19:41.430  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
[gasps]

292
00:19:44.266 --> 00:19:45.517  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
[Joe] Jet.

293
00:19:46.894 --> 00:19:48.604  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
I know you're happy to see me,

294
00:19:48.687 --> 00:19:50.898  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
but no kiss, okay?

295
00:19:50.981 --> 00:19:52.274  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
[chuckles]

296
00:19:53.734 --> 00:19:55.652  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
[Heinrich]
<i>The purge is complete.</i>

297
00:19:55.736 --> 00:19:58.614  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
<i>I've put the micro-drone drop</i>
<i>via the reentry capsules</i>

298
00:19:58.697 --> 00:20:00.073  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
<i>on hold as well.</i>

299
00:20:00.240 --> 00:20:03.202  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
Now we just have to start up
the main engine

300
00:20:03.285 --> 00:20:05.204  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
and then
make our way out, right?

301
00:20:05.287 --> 00:20:07.873  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
004, you need to get over here.

302
00:20:07.956 --> 00:20:09.333  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
[Heinrich] <i>Hold up a second</i>.

303
00:20:10.751 --> 00:20:12.044  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
I think someone's trying

304
00:20:12.127 --> 00:20:14.296  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
to take control
of the station again.

305
00:20:14.379 --> 00:20:15.380  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
[Joe] <i>Wait a minute</i>.

306
00:20:15.464 --> 00:20:17.883  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
<i>The Professor is still alive?</i>

307
00:20:17.966 --> 00:20:20.469  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
These are talents
we've already seen,

308
00:20:20.552 --> 00:20:23.305  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
but it's a different member
of The Blessed.

309
00:20:23.388 --> 00:20:26.600  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
No wavering
in his emotions at all.

310
00:20:26.767 --> 00:20:28.727  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
Another member of The Blessed?

311
00:20:28.810 --> 00:20:29.853  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
Where is he?

312
00:20:30.020 --> 00:20:31.355  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
I detect nothing.

313
00:20:31.438 --> 00:20:33.607  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
There's no sign of anyone else
in the station.

314
00:20:33.774 --> 00:20:36.318  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
In that case,
it's coming from Earth!

315
00:20:36.485 --> 00:20:38.779  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
[Jet] Damn it. After all that,

316
00:20:38.862 --> 00:20:40.906  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
we're right back
to where we started?

317
00:20:40.989 --> 00:20:44.284  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
No. We can still do this

318
00:20:44.451 --> 00:20:47.120  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
<i>if we can get the engine</i>
<i>started before he takes over</i>

319
00:20:47.204 --> 00:20:49.289  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
<i>and accelerate</i>
<i>to escape velocity.</i>

320
00:20:49.456 --> 00:20:52.793  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
[Heinrich] <i>Wait a second.</i>
<i>We can still pull this off</i>.

321
00:20:52.876 --> 00:20:55.295  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
<i>I'm putting in</i>
<i>the final trajectory.</i>

322
00:20:55.379 --> 00:20:58.131  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
<i>I'll head over</i>
<i>as soon as I'm done with that.</i>

323
00:20:58.298 --> 00:21:01.009  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
[Joe] <i>Gotcha.</i>
<i>Better get cracking, Heinrich</i>.

324
00:21:01.093 --> 00:21:02.636  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
-[gasps]
-[Heinrich] <i>Right</i>.

325
00:21:02.719 --> 00:21:05.806  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
<i>Hey, could you two go check</i>
<i>on the escape capsule?</i>

326
00:21:05.973 --> 00:21:08.392  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
<i>We've made it this far.</i>
<i>Last thing we want</i>

327
00:21:08.475 --> 00:21:10.310  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
<i>is to end up</i>
<i>burned to a crisp.</i>

328
00:21:13.939 --> 00:21:15.482  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
[Joe] <i>Everything looks fine</i>.

329
00:21:15.565 --> 00:21:16.566  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
[Jet] <i>Yeah</i>.

330
00:21:16.650 --> 00:21:18.568  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
[Heinrich] <i>Thanks.</i>
<i>That's good to know.</i>

331
00:21:19.903 --> 00:21:20.904  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
[Jet] <i>Wait. What</i>?

332
00:21:21.071 --> 00:21:24.074  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
[Joe] <i>004, what's going on</i>?

333
00:21:24.157 --> 00:21:25.575  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
[Heinrich] <i>I'm sorry</i>,

334
00:21:25.659 --> 00:21:28.120  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
<i>but there's no way</i>
<i>I can leave here now.</i>

335
00:21:28.203 --> 00:21:29.705  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
[Jet] <i>What are</i>
<i>you talking about</i>?

336
00:21:29.871 --> 00:21:33.292  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
The moment I disconnect,
whoever that Blessed is

337
00:21:33.375 --> 00:21:36.211  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
will doubtless try
to take control of the station.

338
00:21:36.378 --> 00:21:39.715  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
<i>It's not just failing</i>
<i>to deflect it away from Earth.</i>

339
00:21:39.881 --> 00:21:43.677  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
<i>It'll also set the micro-drones</i>
<i>operation back in motion.</i>

340
00:21:43.760 --> 00:21:46.680  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
<i>And besides,</i>
<i>I've already made up my mind</i>

341
00:21:46.763 --> 00:21:49.224  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
<i>to pilot this station</i>
<i>to the very end.</i>

342
00:21:49.391 --> 00:21:51.476  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
Just hang on.
I'm coming to get you!

343
00:21:51.560 --> 00:21:53.186  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
-[Joe grunting]
-[Heinrich] <i>Stop it</i>!

344
00:21:54.563 --> 00:21:56.481  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
<i>There's no more time.</i>

345
00:21:56.565 --> 00:21:59.192  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
Come on. There's no way
you'll be able to--

346
00:22:00.319 --> 00:22:01.695  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
'Til next time.

347
00:22:03.405 --> 00:22:05.782  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
[Joe] <i>No, Heinrich! Don't do it</i>!

348
00:22:05.866 --> 00:22:07.826  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
<i>There's got to be another way.</i>

349
00:22:08.910 --> 00:22:10.537  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
But there's not.

350
00:22:10.620 --> 00:22:12.289  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
Farewell, my friends.

351
00:22:29.431 --> 00:22:34.186  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
Heinrich, no!

352
00:23:11.973 --> 00:23:13.975  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
[ballad playing]

353
00:23:21.691 --> 00:23:23.693  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
[singing in Japanese]

